title: Beauty Trends From 2007 That Should Never Make A Comeback
text:
ID: 10340316 2. A heavy load of bronzer and self-tanner because we all slightly resembled orange peels. beaniegram2000 / Via ebay.com
Kevin Winter / Getty Images
 ID: 10340267 3. Bright ass eyeshadow because it was just too extra. colossalfinds / Via ebay.com

 ID: 10340740 4. Frosted pink lipstick because it was a color that looked good on so few. phonelinksuk / Via ebay.com
Toby Canham / Getty
 ID: 10340610 5. Clear glossy lips because that shit was terrible when the wind accidentally blew your hair into your mouth. cosme-de / Via ebay.com
Charley Gallay
 ID: 10340992 6. Lining your waterline in heavy black eyeliner because it was always smudged under your eyes within an hour of applying. infinityscents / Via ebay.com
Charley Gallay / Getty
 ID: 10340385 7. Thin and over-tweezed eyebrows because WHY??? Noel Vasquez / Getty Images
Evan Agostini / Getty
 ID: 10340544 8. Super smokey eye for both a day and night look because we just need to pick a lane. mercedes3918 / Via ebay.com
Scott Gries / Getty
 ID: 10340432 9. Colored eyeliner because it was always a little bit overboard. cosme-de / Via ebay.com
Scott Gries / Getty
 ID: 10341103 10. Curling the fuck out of your wispy eyelashes because they were way too dramatic. Evan Agostini / Getty Images
Michael Buckner / Getty
 ID: 10340471 11. Thick as hell eyeliner because it was all just too much. pharmapacks / Via ebay.com
Ethan Miller / Getty
 ID: 10340272 12. Magenta lipstick because you’d always find a bit on your front teeth. bransdeals2015 / Via ebay.com
Mark Mainz / Getty
